- The game has a 3 x 3 grid.
- Players must select their mark before the game starts
- Winning is either diagonally, vertically or horizontally.
- if neither player has a straight line of 3 marks, it is considered a tie.

Requirements;

- initialize_board
- print_board
- make_move(player, row, col)
- check_winner()
- check_draw()
- is_valid_move(row, col)
- is_game_over()
- reset_board()
- play_game()


+ board
+ current_player
+ winner
+ game_over
+ draw